xt-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-6 pb-3 border-b-2 border-blue-600\">Raw & Chilled</h3>\n                    <div class=\"space-y-5\">\n                        <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm border-l-4 border-blue-500\">\n                            <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1\">Ceviche Trio</h4>\n                            <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-2\">Marinated fish, shrimp, scallops with citrus</p>\n                            <p class=\"text-blue-600 font-bold\">$26</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm border-l-4 border-blue-500\">\n                            <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1\">Oyster Platter</h4>\n                            <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-2\">Selection of 12 fresh oysters with mignonette</p>\n                            <p class=\"text-blue-600 font-bold\">$28</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm border-l-4 border-blue-500\">\n                            <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1\">Sashimi Selection</h4>\n                            <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-2\">Premium fish sliced to order</p>\n                            <p class=\"text-blue-600 font-bold\">$32</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-6 pb-3 border-b-2 border-blue-600\">Grilled & Hot</h3>\n                    <div class=\"space-y-5\">\n                        <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm border-l-4 border-blue-500\">\n                            <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1\">Branzino</h4>\n                            <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-2\">Whole grilled Mediterranean sea bass, lemon & herbs</p>\n                            <p class=\"tex